"\xa0Improve\xa0education\xa0service\xa0delivery\xa0and\xa0youth\xa0employability . Improvements\xa0in\xa0basic\xa0education\xa0and\xa0market?responsive\xa0skills\xa0are\xa0combined\xa0in\xa0one\xa0objective\xa0as\xa0both\xa0are\xa0critical\xa0complimentary\xa0inputs\xa0 aimed\xa0at\xa0ensuring\xa0better\xa0access\xa0of\xa0youth\xa0to\xa0more\xa0productive\xa0employment\xa0opportunities.\xa0Education\xa0and\xa0market?responsive\xa0skills\xa0are\xa0also\xa0critical\xa0for\xa0the\xa0 economic\xa0transformation\xa0sought\xa0by\xa0the\xa0Government,\xa0and\xa0for\xa0ensuring\xa0that\xa0benefits\xa0from\xa0growth\xa0reach\xa0the\xa0poorest\xa0and\xa0are\xa0equitably\xa0shared.\xa0As\xa0pointed\xa0 out\xa0in\xa0the\xa0SCD,\xa0C\xf4te\xa0d\x92Ivoire\x92s\xa0education\xa0system,\xa0including\xa0technical\xa0and\xa0vocational\xa0training,\xa0has\xa0suffered\xa0from\xa0weak\xa0governance,\xa0lack\xa0of\xa0a\xa0clearly\xa0defined\xa0 mission,\xa0and\xa0poor\xa0linkages\xa0with\xa0private\xa0sector\xa0stakeholders\xa0and\xa0labor\xa0market\xa0needs.\xa0Improving\xa0youth\xa0employability\xa0will\xa0require\xa0close\xa0collaboration\xa0between\xa0 institutions\xa0in\xa0charge\xa0of\xa0skill\xa0development,\xa0labor\xa0market\xa0policies,\xa0financial\xa0institutions,\xa0and\xa0the\xa0private\xa0sector\xa0to\xa0address\xa0the\xa0multiple\xa0constraints\xa0to\xa0higher\xa0 productivity\xa0in\xa0key\xa0economic\xa0sectors.\xa0The\xa0Government\x92s\xa0employment\xa0policy\xa0aims\xa0to\xa0encourage\xa0<span id = "word">Job</span>\xa0creation\xa0in\xa0the\xa0private\xa0sector\xa0by\xa0supporting\xa0specialized\xa0 training,\xa0calls\xa0for\xa0universal\xa0primary\xa0education,\xa0youth\xa0training\xa0consistent\xa0with\xa0labor\xa0market\xa0needs;\xa0and\xa0expansion\xa0of\xa0vocational\xa0training\xa0to\xa0improve\xa0labor\xa0 productivity.\xa0Building\xa0on\xa0the\xa0successful\xa0Youth\xa0Employment\xa0Project,\xa0the\xa0WBG\xa0will\xa0expand\xa0its\xa0support\xa0to\xa0address\xa